<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4550168>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 8. Clathrocaspia brotzkajae (Starobogatov in Anistratenko & Prisjazhnjuk, 1992) from the Middle Caspian Basin. (a, b) Holotype, locality 10 (ZIN 1). (c) Paratype, locality 12 (ZIN, no number). (d, k, l) Paratype, locality 12 (ZIN, no number). (e) Paratype, locality 12 (ZIN, no number). (f) Paratype, locality 12 (ZIN, no number). (g–i) Specimen labelled as “Caspia alighadzhievi, holotype”, locality 6 (ZIN, no number). (j, m) Specimen labelled as “Caspia alighadzhievi, paratype”, locality 11 (ZIN, no number). Scale bars = 1 mm (a–k), 100 μm (l, m)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4550168/files/figure.png" .

